<%- include("partials/heading") -%>

<div class="gameTitle">
  <h1>Simon Game</h1>
  <h3 id="level-title">Press any key to start</h3>
  </div>

  <p>
  <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseExample" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseExample">
    How to play
  </button>
</p>
<div class="collapse" id="collapseExample">
  <div class="card card-body gameText">
    Once the game has started a button will be selected and you need to press the selected button. Each one you get right another will be selected and you need to click all the buttons in the correct order. Good Luck!
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">

      <div type="button" id="orange" class="btn btn2 orange">

        </div>
        <div type="button" id="green" class="btn btn2 green">

          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div type="button" id="blue" class="btn btn2 blue">

          </div>
          <div type="button" id="purple" class="btn btn2 purple">

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="JavaScript/game.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
    </body>
    </html>
